  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc1 ; \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf - \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tamil Nadu Government's Relief Relief Scheme Completed; Thanks to Tamil Nadu Government - Senthil Thondaman",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Labor Congress President Senthil Thondaman has said that the last ship containing relief goods has arrived in the country today under the Tamil Nadu government's dry food distribution program for the people of Sri Lanka who are facing economic crises and the distribution activities have started.",
        "He said this while attending a press conference held today at the main party office of the Sri Lanka Labor Congress.",
        "Dry food products were supplied to Sri Lanka in various stages by a group including the Chief Minister of Tamil Nadu",
        "In this regard, we thank the Chief Minister of Tamil Nadu and all those who have helped the people of India.",
        "Accordingly, a total of 40,000 metric tons of rice, 102 metric tons of pharmaceutical products and 500 metric tons of dairy products have been sent to Sri Lanka so far from India.",
        "Accordingly, relief dry food items have been provided to 23 lakh families in Sri Lanka so far. It has been distributed to 25 districts across Sri Lanka",
        "The last ship loaded with dry food products provided by the Tamil Nadu government reached the country today. Actions have been taken to provide the poor families who have not received the relief items already.",
        "And based on this, the Tamil Nadu Government's scheme of providing relief goods has been completed.",
        "Based on that, on behalf of the people of Sri Lanka, I would like to thank the Chief Minister of Tamil Nadu and the people of India."
      ],
